articles.description: Will Curry's incredible shooting become the new normal for more guards like the OU star? Kevin Pelton examines what Young shows about the NBA MVP's effect on future draft prospects.
articles.headline: Is Trae Young just the first of many Steph Curry clones?

articles.description: Trae Young's sudden struggles is the biggest question in the Big 12. In the SEC, it's a daily struggle for Kentucky. As March approaches, each league has some big things to figure out over the next two weeks.

articles.description: It wasn't that long ago that Pitt was an NCAA tournament mainstay. Now, the Panthers are 0-13 in the ACC. Kevin Stallings thinks he can turn things around, but will he even get the chance?

videos.description: Cincinnati's Kyle Washington spots up from beyond the arc and drains a three over the Western Carolina defender as the Bearcats are rolling early up 28-10.
videos.headline: Washington drains triple, adding to Cincinnati fast start

videos.description: The Bearcats' offense whips the ball around in transition and Mamoudou Diarra finds a window to receive the pass and slams it down.
videos.headline: Ball movement frees Diarra for slam

videos.description: Tre Scott draws a double team in the post and frees Cane Broome who drains the triple as the Bearcats lead 69-35.
videos.headline: Scott passes out of post to set up three

videos.description: Cincinnati's Tre Scott flashes to the top of the key and brings his defender into the post where he finishes with the foul as the Bearcats lead 98-46.
videos.headline: Scott battles in post and gets and-1
